name: Committed
description: Shows up, stays steady, finishes what they start—especially when unnoticed.

name: Patient
description: Keeps a calm pace through long shifts and difficult situations.

name: Over-Skilled
description: Carries talents beyond current role; quietly masters details others miss.

name: Dependable
description: Reliability keeps teams and systems running; rarely misses beats.

name: Observant
description: Reads surroundings and people, seeing needs and risks early.

name: Service-Minded
description: Takes pride in helping; sees service as strength and calling.

name: Resilient
description: Adapts to unpredictable schedules, conditions, and attitudes.

name: Protective
description: Carries a sense of duty for people, property, and process.

name: Team-Grounded
description: Thrives in coordination—crews, shifts, and teams.

name: Growth-Driven
description: Quiet ambition to advance, train, or build something of their own.
